[{"create-time":1737972142375,"title":"January 27th, 2025",":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":log/id":1737972142374,"children":[{"string":"14:02","uid":"CPHFEOVYz","create-time":1737972148000,"edit-time":1737972150082,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"[[spreadsheet brain]]","create-time":1737985699174,":block/refs":[{":block/uid":"hXfA6Pkp8"}],"refs":[{"uid":"hXfA6Pkp8"}],":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"uid":"wMTluZbAg","edit-time":1737985703227,":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"[[the more someone optimizes for social power, the more vulnerable they become to social control]] #Maybe","create-time":1737984928930,":block/refs":[{":block/uid":"q88vW2uMc"},{":block/uid":"6kdX0ZYWy"}],"refs":[{"uid":"q88vW2uMc"},{"uid":"6kdX0ZYWy"}],":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"uid":"FD6yPC17T","edit-time":1737984938288,":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"Babe,","create-time":1737972151422,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"children":[{"string":"It's been a tumultuous week for me. I've had more access to my emotions than usual. Being away from you gave me time and space to reflect, in ways I didn't expect. Namely, a question I never considered planted itself in a patch of soil that I have been avoiding. And now it's taking over the garden. And as you can tell from the last few days, I'm trying to face it head-on. I want to come out of this screaming, I KNOW WHAT TO DO. AND IF I DON'T IT'll STILL BE OK. ","uid":"fzszyeKHq","create-time":1737972192871,"edit-time":1737973366090,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"I believe that our most important goal is to be the fullest version of yourself you can be, no matter the cost. \"You are who you are, don't keep you waiting.\" I believe that if you're not egoistical in this way- that if you deny yourself this exploration and pursuit of the self- it comes back to hurt those around you. I believe that relationships must be based on realistic constraints; that they must truly make both of you better; that it might not come easy, but it sure as fuck mustn't come apart easy either. That you can each be perfectly good people alone, yet a disastrous match for each other. <in freudian terms, you can't deny the id; it should be satisfied and congruent with the ego; this matters more than the superego>","uid":"NeA8bTZfA","create-time":1737972358387,"edit-time":1737973428694,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"Um... anyway. The question that popped up in my head that I've been unable to vanquish: How can Dilnaz and you spend time together when you're far apart? And the insidious follow-up question: Do you and Dilnaz fundamentally desire different things when you're in your own head / alone?","uid":"F91JhJ3--","create-time":1737973249687,"edit-time":1737993294218,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"I will explain how I've been trying to answer this question. ","create-time":1737973796783,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"children":[{"edit-time":1737974138196,"children":[{"string":"The things we do together must be better than what we could do alone. ","uid":"I6bnlFZ6c","create-time":1737973983793,"edit-time":1737973983793,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"The things we do must work within our schedules/environment/energy levels. ","create-time":1737974117532,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"children":[{"string":"This is less important because the latter can be worked around, but important to note regardless. ","uid":"mnGg4Vtzw","create-time":1737973813196,"edit-time":1737974117535,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}}],"uid":"pKe12lPY5","edit-time":1737974117532,":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}}],"refs":[{"uid":"Q-ZRm9l5u"}],"uid":"sI8SjF8CO",":block/refs":[{":block/uid":"Q-ZRm9l5u"}],"string":"Constraints::",":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"create-time":1737973982169,":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"The obvious first answer is talking. ","create-time":1737974192972,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"children":[{"string":"**[[Counterpoint]]**: You can only talk for so long (20m- 2 hours depending on the day) before it starts failing [constraint 1](((I6bnlFZ6c))). Some things cannot be properly expressed through talking alone. ","create-time":1737973932107,":block/refs":[{":block/uid":"UhqOJ79YV"},{":block/uid":"I6bnlFZ6c"}],"refs":[{"uid":"UhqOJ79YV"},{"uid":"I6bnlFZ6c"}],":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"uid":"ol_zS4NmX","edit-time":1737974275330,":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}}],"uid":"SPzx_iiX3","edit-time":1737974192972,":edit/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"}},{"string":"Things that came up but that I ruled out: ","create-time":1737973945035,"heading":3,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"children":[{"string":"**Watching movies/shows/YT videos**","create-time":1737974159129,":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"children":[{"string":"Pros:: Low energy requirement ","create-time":1737974341199,":block/refs":[{":block/uid":"GNWSsXm81"}],"refs":[{"uid":"GNWSsXm81"}],":create/user":{":user/uid":"eyxGl1TJWCTcRVSJVJDyoLzWVqk2"},"uid":"HICm0M9vZ","edit-time":1737974351812,":